The director and owner of Grupo Nuaria, the lawyer and businessman Manuel N.A., was arrested in Nigrán (Pontevedra), as was Pablo José M.G., director of Suelo de Inmonuar, an agency integrated into the Group, and through which the bribes would have been made.
